#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.88"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.88:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.88:0.2"
msgid "9. Macalavagga "
msgstr "9. Confirmed "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: samaṇamacala-saññojanasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.88:0.3"
msgid "88. Saṃyojanasutta "
msgstr "88. Fetters "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.88:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, these four people are found in the world. "

msgctxt "an4.88:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "an4.88:1.3"
msgid "Samaṇamacalo, samaṇapuṇḍarīko, samaṇapadumo, samaṇesu samaṇasukhumālo. "
msgstr "The confirmed ascetic, the white lotus ascetic, the pink lotus ascetic, and the exquisite ascetic of ascetics. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.89, sc2
msgctxt "an4.88:2.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo samaṇamacalo hoti? "
msgstr "And how is a person a confirmed ascetic? "

msgctxt "an4.88:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu tiṇṇaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā sotāpanno hoti avinipātadhammo niyato sambodhiparāyaṇo. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant—with the ending of three fetters—is a stream-enterer, not liable to be reborn in the underworld, bound for awakening. "

msgctxt "an4.88:2.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo samaṇamacalo hoti. "
msgstr "That’s how a person is a confirmed ascetic. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.88:3.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo samaṇapuṇḍarīko hoti? "
msgstr "And how is a person a white lotus ascetic? "

msgctxt "an4.88:3.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu tiṇṇaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā, rāgadosamohānaṃ tanuttā sakadāgāmī hoti, sakideva imaṃ lokaṃ āgantvā dukkhassantaṃ karoti. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant—with the ending of three fetters, and the weakening of greed, hate, and delusion—is a once-returner. They come back to this world once only, then make an end of suffering. "

msgctxt "an4.88:3.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo samaṇapuṇḍarīko hoti. "
msgstr "That’s how a person is a white lotus ascetic. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.88:4.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo samaṇapadumo hoti? "
msgstr "And how is a person a pink lotus ascetic? "

msgctxt "an4.88:4.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu pañcannaṃ orambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā opapātiko hoti tattha parinibbāyī anāvattidhammo tasmā lokā. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant—with the ending of the five lower fetters—is reborn spontaneously. They’re extinguished there, and are not liable to return from that world. "

msgctxt "an4.88:4.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo samaṇapadumo hoti. "
msgstr "That’s how a person is a pink lotus ascetic. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.88:5.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo samaṇesu samaṇasukhumālo hoti? "
msgstr "And how is a person an exquisite ascetic of ascetics? "

msgctxt "an4.88:5.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant realizes the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in this very life. And they live having realized it with their own insight due to the ending of defilements. "

msgctxt "an4.88:5.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo samaṇesu samaṇasukhumālo hoti. "
msgstr "That’s how a person is an exquisite ascetic of ascetics. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.88:5.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmin”ti. "
msgstr "These are the four people found in the world.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.88:5.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

